---
title: "_applyAssetParamsUpdates (BaseAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_empty: adds.length == 0 and removes.length == 0?
    q_check_empty --> q_revert_empty: both empty
    q_revert_empty --> [*]: revert EmptyList
    q_check_empty --> q_iter_removes: at least one non-empty
    q_iter_removes --> q_check_remove_live: for i in removes
    q_check_remove_live --> q_revert_live: asset has live auction or (asset == assetOut and liveAuctionExists)
    q_revert_live --> [*]: revert LiveAuction
    q_check_remove_live --> q_check_remove_set: no live auction conflict
    q_check_remove_set --> q_revert_not_set: assetParams.decimals == 0
    q_revert_not_set --> [*]: revert AssetParamsNotSet
    q_check_remove_set --> q_do_remove: assetParams.decimals > 0
    q_do_remove --> q_iter_removes: delete s_assetParams[asset], emit AssetParamsRemoved
    q_iter_removes --> q_iter_adds: removes loop complete
    q_iter_adds --> q_check_add_live: for i in adds
    q_check_add_live --> q_revert_live_add: asset has live auction or (asset == assetOut and liveAuctionExists)
    q_revert_live_add --> [*]: revert LiveAuction
    q_check_add_live --> q_check_allowlist: no live auction conflict
    q_check_allowlist --> q_revert_not_allowed: not allowlisted
    q_revert_not_allowed --> [*]: revert AssetNotAllowlisted
    q_check_allowlist --> q_check_decimals: allowlisted
    q_check_decimals --> q_revert_decimals: params.decimals != actual decimals
    q_revert_decimals --> [*]: revert InvalidAssetDecimals
    q_check_decimals --> q_check_min_size: decimals match
    q_check_min_size --> q_revert_zero: minAuctionSizeUsd == 0
    q_revert_zero --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroValue
    q_check_min_size --> q_check_is_out: minAuctionSizeUsd > 0
    q_check_is_out --> q_store: asset == assetOut (skip auction-specific validation)
    q_check_is_out --> q_check_duration: asset != assetOut
    q_check_duration --> q_revert_dur: auctionDuration == 0
    q_revert_dur --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroValue
    q_check_duration --> q_check_ending: auctionDuration > 0
    q_check_ending --> q_revert_ending: endingPriceMultiplier < minPriceMultiplier
    q_revert_ending --> [*]: revert InvalidEndingPriceMultiplier
    q_check_ending --> q_check_starting: endingPriceMultiplier >= minPriceMultiplier
    q_check_starting --> q_revert_starting: endingPriceMultiplier > startingPriceMultiplier
    q_revert_starting --> [*]: revert StartingPriceMultiplierLowerThanEndingPriceMultiplier
    q_check_starting --> q_store: startingPriceMultiplier >= endingPriceMultiplier
    q_store --> q_iter_adds: s_assetParams[asset] = assetParams, emit AssetParamsUpdated
    q_iter_adds --> [*]: adds loop complete

    note right of q_check_is_out
        INV-001: assetOut only requires minAuctionSizeUsd and decimals
        INV-002: Non-assetOut assets require valid duration and price multipliers
        INV-003: startingPriceMultiplier >= endingPriceMultiplier >= minPriceMultiplier
        INV-004: Cannot modify params of assets with live auctions
        INV-005: Asset must be allowlisted before params can be set
        INV-006: Provided decimals must match on-chain ERC20 decimals
    end note
